Closes-Bug: #1281127

Remove redundant list from v3 attach_interface API

Current body of v3 "attach_interface create" API is defined like:
  {
      "interface_attachment": {
          "net_id": <uuid>,
          "port_id": <uuid>,
          "fixed_ips": [
              {"ip_address": <ip_address>}
          ]
      }
   }

"fixed_ips" attribute is defined with a list, but Nova looks only the
first entry of the list. So it is better to remove the list from the
attribute for representing the attribute structure clearly.

Partially implements blueprint nova-v3-api

